{"tid":1748183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「爆眼少女」人像照登《紐時》頭版　「身處極權社會才被迫以鮮血守衛」","createTime":"2019-11-23T14:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T14:28:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8cdcbe8c057aa857ca776912fbd6044c8de43ab","tid":1748183,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/newyorktimes-12_JhimM_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fnewyorktimes-12_JhimM_1200x0.png&h=cb2c9270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反送中運動至今逾 5 個月，美國《紐約時報》明日頭版將刊登 8.11 在尖沙咀被警方布袋彈打中右眼的女義務急救員人像照片。報道中「爆眼少女」化名為 K，並表示「唯有在一個極權、扭曲的社會，人們才會被迫以生命及鮮血保衛它。」<br />\n<br />\n該《紐時》圖片專題名為 Hong Kong: A City Divided，由香港攝影師林亦非操刀。報道為多名運動抗爭者拍攝人像照，當中包括黃之鋒、周庭、陳日君、岑子杰等知名人士，亦有不少人戴頭盔、豬嘴上鏡；該專題亦有建制派葉劉淑儀、劉兆佳的「大頭相」。<br />\n<br />\n攝影師林亦非今日在 facebook 稱，相片於影樓拍攝，而右眼中彈少女的相片，則是明天美國《紐時》頭版。林亦非亦問，「六個月來，這場運動中出現過的每一張臉，你又記得多少？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%88%86%E7%9C%BC%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3-%E4%BA%BA%E5%83%8F%E7%85%A7%E7%99%BB-%E7%B4%90%E6%99%82-%E9%A0%AD%E7%89%88-%E8%BA%AB%E8%99%95%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%89%8D%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%AB%E4%BB%A5%E9%AE%AE%E8%A1%80%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%259C%25BC%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2583%258F%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2599%25BB-%25E7%25B4%2590%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%2589%2588-%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2589%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E8%25A1%2580%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%259B%2F&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fs%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=470c9f25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%259C%25BC%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2583%258F%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2599%25BB-%25E7%25B4%2590%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%2589%2588-%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2589%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E8%25A1%2580%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%259B%2F&h=4507bc4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%88%86%E7%9C%BC%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3-%E4%BA%BA%E5%83%8F%E7%85%A7%E7%99%BB-%E7%B4%90%E6%99%82-%E9%A0%AD%E7%89%88-%E8%BA%AB%E8%99%95%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%89%8D%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%AB%E4%BB%A5%E9%AE%AE%E8%A1%80%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%9B/</a>"},{"pid":"e8f22d49a98210723c6040afed976d1fd12108ef","tid":1748183,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:21:47.000Z","msg":"11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yQUK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yQUK2.png&h=727d0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等候時及面對<span style=\"color: red;\">白警</span>時唱<strong>《Sing Hallelujah To The Lord》</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港區 6:00pm 灣仔紅隧入口集合，大量兩層巴士接過紅隧，或自行行過紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【急】請傳給撞區候選人！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>活動申請不反通知書，先發表就出線有票，遲發表要退選。</span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fs%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=b1e5d44e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、所有民主派議員、及候選人。〔民主派即是所有推動民主，包括本土及泛民〕<br />\n<br />\n<span s